@NODE 1.0 "Introduction"


This program allows you to surf from one screen  to another 
A Little window come in the frontscreen with a gadtool 
list gadget. Click on the name of the screen, and this
screen go on the front. 

	This program is a commodity. 
	
The normal HotKey is F4
The normal HotKey for config is Ctrl F4 
The normal HotKey for quit is left alt F4
The normal Hotkey for the window is F5
 


@ENDNODE

@NODE 1.1 "Features"


     Support all worbench screen mode

     Supports @{" Tooltypes        " Link 4.1}
     
     From the v 0.11 it is localized

@ENDNODE


@NODE 2.0 "Requirements"




     Minimum:
     
     A Amiga with OS 3 

     68000


     Recommended:

     68020


@ENDNODE

@NODE 2.1 "Installation"

Use the Install utility or

Just copy ScreenSurf Anywere 

For use clic on there Icon. A litle window
appear for few second and disappear.


For active this commodity hit the popkey 
(f4 by default) choose the screen.

For quit this commodity hit quit popkey 
(left alt f4 by default)

For Config this commodity hit the popkey (lalt F4 by default)

For active the window utilities hit the popkey
(F5 by default)

see @{" Introduction     " Link 1.0

or @{" Tooltypes        " Link 4.1}



@ENDNODE

